Class DisposableFlowable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reactivex.Flowable<T>
      • hu.akarnokd.rxjava2.async.DisposableFlowable<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the value type of the sequence
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.reactivex.disposables.Disposable, org.reactivestreams.Publisher<T>

    public abstract class DisposableFlowable<T>
extends io.reactivex.Flowable<T>
implements io.reactivex.disposables.Disposable
    A Flowable that also offers a means to dispose it, cancelling/disposing some shared underlying computation or resource via Disposable.dispose().
